snippet.title: REAL MADRID Oyo Sports Building Play Set UNBOXING RONALDO MESSI Figure Kids Toys Review
snippet.description:
Lucas is unboxing new toys and reviewing REAL MADRID GAMDAY Field Building Play Set from Oyo Sports. Plus, we have other sets and toys for kids to show featuring Manchester City and FC Barcelona players. Check out our toy unboxing video and a review of OYO SPORTS BUILDING SETS and Collectors Set with your favorite soccer player figures including Messi, Ronaldo and Neymar Jr. The Real Madrid Gameday Field Set and smaller Manchester City Playmaker Set bring the game of soccer to life by offering hands-on building and play experiences for kids to create game-action replays or new imaginative soccer moments. The OYO Sports soccer play sets are available for other favorite soccer clubs.
The Real Madrid GAMEDAY Field Building Play Set brings the soccer stadium experience to life through realistic soccer field features and the interactive functions of the buildable set. Designed with score board, buildable goals, player benches and corner flags the field set replicates true game-action play. The Real Madrid GAMEDAY Field Building Play Set comes with 330 blocks and 6 soccer player poseable figures including Christiano Ronaldo. The Real Madrid GAMEDAY Field Building Play Set has an authentic team logo at score board and on corner flags a buildable field play surface that works with other major brands like LEGO.

The Manchester City Buildable Playmaker Set comes with a practice field featuring buildable goal, 2 corner flags and scoreboard. Plus, you can decorate your Manchester City Buildable Playmaker Set with team’s logo. This set comes wuth 3 Oyo Sports minifigures including Sergio Aguero, Claudio Bravo and an Official Refeeee. The Manchester City Buildable Playmaker Set The set has 100 pieces and is for kids of ages 6+.

The FC Barcelona Collector Set offers 5 Oyo Sports minifigures including MESSI, NEYMAR JR, PIQUE, TIER STEGEN and SUAREZ. The set comes also with team logo. This is a perfect start to collect and build your ultimate soccer team!

About OYO Sports. Oyo Sports is the leading manufacturer of licensed sports minifigures across the major U.S. sports leagues, including MLB, NFL, NHL, MLS and over 60 colleges. OYO Sports minifigures look, act and play like your favorite major league players.  Each minifigure has real life characteristics and traits of the athletes they portray, including player likeness, bendable knees, rotating forearms, and the ability to hold sporting equipment. OYO Sports make great gifts for any sports fan young and old!
